      <title>最高法院在很大程度上支持Biden-er-fda在调味vap上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/supreme-court-largely-backs-biden-era-fda-on-flavored-vapes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院在很大程度上支持食品和药物管理局在拒绝出售风味蒸发产品的申请方面，支持该机构在乔·拜登（Joe Biden）担任总统期间对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）采取这种方法的不确定性的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/supreme-court-largely-backs-biden-era-fda-on-flavored-vapes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 14:24:29 GMT</pubDate>
